text: Galícia Esporte Clube is a Brazilian football club which plays in Salvador da Bahía, Brazil. == Honors == Bahia League Championship (Campeonato Baiano) Champion: 1937, 1941, 1942, 1943 and 1968. Runner-up: 1935, 1936, 1938, 1939, 1940, 1967, 1980, 1982 and 1995. Bahia League Championship Second Level (Campeonato Baiano Segunda Divisão) Champion: 1985, 1988 and 2013. Runner-up: 2007.
